Silken Ward
Discworld ritual help
Silken Ward

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Silken Ward -- Creates a bond between you and an object.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Silken ward calls upon your God to infuse an object with the desire to stay
with you. If the object is taken from you, it will ask you to come and get it
back for a period of time. 
.EP
